    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304770/extras/e97fd1ef11d7986d10bd72869de3da7a.poster.avif?t=1761371392\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304770/extras/e97fd1ef11d7986d10bd72869de3da7a.webm?t=1761371392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304770/extras/e97fd1ef11d7986d10bd72869de3da7a.mp4?t=1761371392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304770/extras/86c7293284faf173ef0bb4207b274263.avif?t=1761371392\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为一名写实主播，莱卡在近一年的内容创作中始终没能取得多大成就。然而，在一次直播中经历了一场尴尬的意外后，她的聊天室却沸腾了！几笔慷慨的打赏接踵而来，紧接着她发现自己的订阅人数竟然涨了！为了迎合新订阅者的期待，莱卡决定扩大自己的创作范围，开始发布视频内容。然而，她需要灵感和点子来让自己的内容更有吸引力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她能实现成为名人的目标吗？在这段内容创作之旅中，她的成长又会如何展开？欢迎来到这款以角色为核心的主播题材RPG，一起揭晓答案！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304770/extras/b72f831027570dec4808cdbcb7eadc7b.avif?t=1761371392\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演莱卡，管理她的日常活动！在城市中寻找灵感，为创作新视频出谋划策；与观众互动、通过直播吸引粉丝；发布照片吸引社区注意力，并通过社交媒体扩大莱卡的粉丝群体。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304770/extras/1818178532b20be0b6c98a15c02b0e86.avif?t=1761371392\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304770/extras/4926edaf399691166553cf01c384e21f.avif?t=1761371392\" width=616 height=720 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304770/extras/69b73b91a88928ce851c92fd5a0a116e.avif?t=1761371392\" width=616 height=720 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304770/extras/40ddf28da0a9652a709b1d9ef718de8d.avif?t=1761371392\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>管理心态值</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >莱卡的心态值越低，她就越愿意尝试一些“离谱”的活动。想知道能离谱到什么程度？让我们说，几乎没有什么能阻挡她迈向成名的脚步。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>昼夜循环</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >白天制作视频，晚上直播，这就是追逐网络名气的日常！在白天和夜晚之间切换，探索城市、触发各种事件，随着莱卡对内容的探索愈发大胆，更多奇遇等待解锁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>事件与回忆室</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在城市中，莱卡会遇到各式各样的人，从陌生人到忠实粉丝应有尽有。挖掘这些事件，推动她的直播之旅，见证她在视频与直播中搞怪的精彩瞬间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>为制造内容恶搞他人</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在满足观众娱乐需求和避免被整蛊目标发现之间取得平衡。观众越开心，打赏越多；但被整蛊的人警惕性越高，莱卡被抓到的风险就越大，甚至可能被举报！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>学习与提升技能</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从师傅那里学习技能，扩展技能树，克服作为一名小有抱负的内容创作者所面临的各种挑战，为实现她的宏伟目标铺平道路！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
